{"tid":1627023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣新方向］香港人最新溝通技巧","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:05:24.000Z","uid":126608,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe4695442ae1ecd275f02937f2954a6932148fc","tid":1627023,"uid":126608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"要將政府同警察仆街既形象再深化，點解唔將文宣融入日常生活之中，例如話：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「鬧人既時候」</span></span><br />\n不要說： 屌你老母。<br />\n試著說： 屌，林鄭生你出黎嫁仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「催人地既時候」</span></span><br />\n不要說：咁撚慢嫁仆街<br />\n試著說：陳茂波派錢都快撚過你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「被人串個陣」</span></span><br />\n不要說： 洗唔洗咁串呀？<br />\n試著說： 林家超教你講野嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「笑9人個陣」</span></span><br />\n不要說：做人唔好咁on9啦！<br />\n試著說：唔好好似班狗咁個腦裝屎先得嫁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「當別人9up時」</span></span><br />\n不要說：山草藥up得就up咩？<br />\n試著說：你以為自己四點鐘謝sir咩，搵齊資料先啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「被逼ot時」</span></span><br />\n不要說：屌你老母又要ot<br />\n試著說：寧願ot，唔要3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「有豬一般既隊友」</span></span><br />\n不要說：屌，個同事on9嫁<br />\n試著說：美芬同麗芸又黎料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「搵理由遲到」</span></span><br />\n不要說：唔...唔好意思，起身遲左.....<br />\n試著說：Empty R又delay啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「中立撚割席」</span></span><br />\n不要說：核彈都唔割！<br />\n試著說：睇你個樣收左唔少蛇齋餅粽喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以上說話仲難聽過粗口，攻擊力強大，希望大家自由發揮！香港人加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"648f50fb32a3673de5eb6785f0823137e1f3babe","tid":1627023,"uid":126608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},{"pid":"d72f950ff10c10b5e5dc4c2a662f3599ebdf725b","tid":1627023,"uid":126608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"648f50fb32a3673de5eb6785f0823137e1f3babe","tid":1627023,"uid":126608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"c4ae45715284f9fc987dc4febff6dc88eb0d2eb4","tid":1627023,"uid":126608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72f950ff10c10b5e5dc4c2a662f3599ebdf725b","tid":1627023,"uid":126608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"648f50fb32a3673de5eb6785f0823137e1f3babe","tid":1627023,"uid":126608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d9df6136f4188bafa66eabdcc5e118ef755d2070","tid":1627023,"uid":51521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"覺得你好撚柒sor"}]}